headline: EOG Resources to Present at Upcoming Conference
summary: EOG Resources, Inc. (EOG) is scheduled to present at the J.P. Morgan Energy, Power, Renewables and Mining Conference at 10:30 a.m. Central time (11:30 a.m. Eastern time) on Tuesday, June 24. Jeffrey R. Leitzell, Executive Vice President and Chief Operating Officer, will present on behalf of EOG.
